<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink112">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi pācilaic</l>
<l>cerunti tāya viruṅkaḻic cērppaṉ</l>
<l>ṟāṉvarak kāṇkuva nāmē</l>
<l>maṟantō maṉṟa nāṇuṭai neñc -ē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh friend, listen!</l>
<l>We will watch, as the man from the shores</l>
<l>With the dark backwaters</l>
<l>- Where the green leaves of the Cerunti plant spread - comes.</l>
<l>Our hearts that possess shyness</l>
<l>Have indeed forgotten [him]!</l>
</lg>
    </div>
